Installation instruction
========================

Before install this program please install Raspbian Lite OS to SD-CARD.
Do not forget to set hostname and network.

Installation
------------
  pi@raspberry$ sudo apt-get update
  pi@raspberry$ sudo apt-get upgrade
  pi@raspberry$ sudo apt-get install mc wget
  pi@raspberry$ wget --directory-prefix=$HOME/download http://www.szerafingomba.hu/equipments/mm5d/mm5d-sw-0.1-noarch.tar.gz
  pi@raspberry$ cd $HOME/download
  pi@raspberry$ tar -xzf mm5d-sw-0.1-noarch.tar.gz
  pi@raspberry$ cd mm5d-sw-0.1
  pi@raspberry$ ./prepare
  pi@raspberry$ ./install

Configuration
-------------
  mm5d@raspberry$ sudo /etc/init.d/mm5d.sh stop
  mm5d@raspberry$ mm5d-editconf
  mm5d@raspberry$ sudo mm5d-updatestartpage
  mm5d@raspberry$ sudo /etc/init.d/mm5d.sh start

Edit example user's controller program
--------------------------------------
  mm5d@raspberry$ sudo /etc/init.d/mm5d.sh stop
  mm5d@raspberry$ mm5d-editcurrentprog
  mm5d@raspberry$ sudo /etc/init.d/mm5d.sh start
  
  or
  
  mm5d@raspberry$ cd ~/cfg_example/
  mm5d@raspberry$ ./cfg_example.sh
  
Remove
------
  pi@raspberry$ cd mm5d-sw-0.1
  pi@raspberry$ ./uninstall
